e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T01:17:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n剩聽到支持度下跌，唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n主因係cut school同 NHS funding <br />\n加強網上對porn 同言論既限制</blockquote><br />\n即係唔關脫歐事？</blockquote><br />\n仲有dementia tax <br />\n不過好多主流媒體都反brexit 所以吹風唔想佢贏都唔奇</blockquote><br />\n如果唔想佢贏應該作民調作到佢拋離好多，而家咁樣咪姐係比May打告急牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗野諗多層得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出面啲選民無你咁清醒ok ?<br />\n你諗下當日幾多人以為唔會brexit，Hilary 實贏到Trump 你就知唔會咁多選民係逆向思考。<br />\n你留意下英國啲報紙，早排連Corbyn 民望低到仆街都唔多報，近排兩邊拉近啲，就日日大篇幅跟進同分析，吹奏工黨同細黨聯手就可以贏到組聯合政府。"},{"pid":"3b7e5d34b7502ffdcbdc964fbd4d17581dab1cbe","tid":267200,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T01:19:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但點跌都唔代表工黨有機，最多係libdem 多d 票咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個民調係Tory支持度無咩點跌，但Labour係咁升喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/070020_93bc1592f67c206563d121edf501a8d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2F070020_93bc1592f67c206563d121edf501a8d9.jpg&h=f09392be&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n有好多民調做緊，睇間報紙鍾意quote 邊啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前睇過有兩三份又話Tory 跌咗+ 工黨升"},{"pid":"da2ea3a2468fa49aa58650c5ab55593284b683cf","tid":267200,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T09:30:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n剩聽到支持度下跌，唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n主因係cut school同 NHS funding <br />\n加強網上對porn 同言論既限制</blockquote><br />\n即係唔關脫歐事？</blockquote><br />\n仲有dementia tax <br />\n不過好多主流媒體都反brexit 所以吹風唔想佢贏都唔奇</blockquote><br />\n如果唔想佢贏應該作民調作到佢拋離好多，而家咁樣咪姐係比May打告急牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗野諗多層得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出面啲選民無你咁清醒ok ?<br />\n你諗下當日幾多人以為唔會brexit，Hilary 實贏到Trump 你就知唔會咁多選民係逆向思考。<br />\n你留意下英國啲報紙，早排連Corbyn 民望低到仆街都唔多報，近排兩邊拉近啲，就日日大篇幅跟進同分析，吹奏工黨同細黨聯手就可以贏到組聯合政府。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁叫逆向思考？<br />\n<br />\n「屌，Troy就輸啦，個日幾大都要出黎投佢」<br />\n「屌，Tory就輸啦，都係唔好投佢啦」<br />\n<br />\n你估下Tory既支持者見到而家既民調，講以上邊句會合理D？<br />\n<br />\n我唔係話傳媒無立場，The Guardian呢D幫Labour幫到出哂汁，但呢度唔係香港，係UK，未至於仆街到用民調黎吹風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}